@@TJvSpecialFolder
<TITLE TJvSpecialFolder type>
Summary
  Defines the different special system folders available in Windows.
Description
  TJvSpecialFolder is the type for the <LINK TJvFindFilesDialog.SpecialFolder, SpecialFolder> property
  of the TJvFindFilesDialog component. It defines all allowable special folders on the system.

